SCTX - Script Source:
; change static/no havok lanterns into havok-enabled lantern on pickup
ScriptName mwLanternHavocOnScript

ref me

Begin OnActivate Player

	set me to GetBaseObject
	
	if eval(me == 0lightUdeUlanternU07 || me == 0lightUdeUlanternU07U128 || me == 0lightUdeUlanternU07Uwarm)
		PlayerRef.AddItemNS 0lightUdeUlanternU07havoc 1
		Disable
	elseif eval(me == 0lightUdeUlanternU05 || me == 0lightUdeUlanternU05U128UCarry || me == 0lightUdeUlanternU05U200 || me == 0lightUdeUlanternU05UCarry )
		PlayerRef.AddItemNS 0lightUdeUlanternU05havoc 1
		Disable
	else
		Activate player
	endif

	
End

;<CSEBlock>
;<CSECaretPos> 577 </CSECaretPos>
;</CSEBlock>
